<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Received</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Payment Submission Successful</h1>
        
        <div class="status-message success">
            <p>Thank you! Your payment details have been successfully submitted.</p>
            <p>Transaction ID: <strong><%= transactionId %></strong></p>
            <p>We will process your order shortly.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="payment-details">
            <h2>What happens next?</h2>
            <p>Our team will verify your payment details and process your order within 5-30 minutes.</p>
            <p>If there are any issues with your payment, we will contact you directly.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p class="contact">
            For any questions, please <a href="mailto:contact@example.com">contact us</a>
        </p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
            <a href="/" class="btn">Return to Home</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 